### GET PROHIBITION REVIEW APPLICATION
######################################
# Disconnect from VPN to run this command, or run on OpenShift pod.
# Example: http://digitalforms-api.c220ad-dev.svc/digitalforms/c741582c-de28-67e2-e054-00144ffbc109/application/saf-ADP-182-21900104-3004
@correlation_id = {{CORRELATION}}-3004

GET http://{{DFAPI_URL}}/{{application_id}}/application/{{correlation_id}}
Authorization: Basic {{DFAPI_CREDENTIALS}}
Content-Type: application/json



### PATCH PROHIBITION REVIEW APPLICATION
########################################
